---
name: Navigation
description: |
  Main site Navigation organism, with logo, [Menu](/patterns/molecules/menu.html) and [Download Button](/patterns/molecules/download-button.html) molecules.
hidepreview: true
notes: |
  - On wide viewports, the Menu and Download Button molecules are displayed inline.
  - On small viewports, the molecules' visibility is toggled using a navigation icon.
links:
    Navigation Demo: /demos/navigation.html
---

<div class="mzp-c-navigation">
  <div class="mzp-l-content">
    <div class="mzp-c-navigation-content">
      <button class="mzp-c-navigation-menu-button" type="button">Menu</button>
      <div class="mzp-c-navigation-logo"><a href="https://www.mozilla.org/">Mozilla</a></div>
      <div class="mzp-c-navigation-items">
        {{#block "menu"}}
          {{#embed "patterns.molecules.menu.menu"}}{{/embed}}
        {{/block}}
        <div class="mzp-c-navigation-download">
          {{#embed "patterns.molecules.download-button.download-button" class="mzp-c-button-compact"}}
            {{#content "privacy-link"}}{{/content}}
          {{/embed}}
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

